; Coverage for chain.cc --sort with explicit --sort-xacts expression

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Drink    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --sort date --sort-xacts amount
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
                                Expenses:Food                $10.00            0
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Cash                  $-5.00       $-5.00
                                Expenses:Drink                $5.00            0
end test
